Sacred Stone Monastery

Overview

Type: Temple

The Sacred Stone Monastery is where the monks of the Earth cult have taken shelter. Above ground the Monastery is in really good shape. The Heroes know that the Monastery has a below ground level.

Â 

Inside are monks, Ogres, Umber Hulk, and other Earth Creatures.

Description

Story

The heroes came here to investigate the Earth Cult sightings. On entry the heroes stepped into a training room and the Monks took the heroes and killed Josephus. The heroes were held captive in the dungeons of this Monastery for about 5 months. Â The Mud-Bloods broke into the Monastery and rescued the heroes and freed the remaining slaves. Among them was Larrakh.
